lead_paragraph: The affairs and prospects of Cuba are the subject of greatest interest here at this moment. The Gazelle to-day contains a telegraphic dispatch announcing the landing and destruction of the Lopez expedition, in the following terms: The Minister Plenipotentiary of Her Majesty to the Minister of Foreign Affairs. PARIS, Sept. 5--11 1/2 A. M.

headline.main: SPAIN.; The Cuban Question In Spain. From the London Morning Chronicle.
